To connect Alexa to your QA products, follow these steps:
(1). Download our App "I Want Automation" from Google Play or App Store;
(2). Create an account on our App "I Want Automation";
(3). You need to have some smart devices Want Automation at hand;
(4). Set up these devices in our "I Want Automation" App and change the appropriate name for your devices that will be used in the "I Want Automation" Skill;
(5). Download the Alexa App on Android or iOS;
(6). Set up Echo with the Alexa App;
(7). Search for the "I Want Automation" Skill in the Skills category of the Alexa App;
(8). Click on Activate Skill from "I Want Automation", and you will be directed to the login page I want Automation;
(9). Enter your username and password of the Quero Automação account, you will be directed to the success page;
(10). That's it! You can enjoy voice control on your devices like these:
"Alexa, turn on the bedroom light."
"Alexa, turn off the bedroom light."
"Alexa, adjust the brightness of the bedroom light by 50 percent."
"Alexa, brighten up the room."
"Alexa, dim the light in the room by 50."
"Alexa, change the bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, make the lights in the room cooler."
